<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Inspiration Board</title>
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg1:#0f172a;
      --bg2:#1e293b;
      --card:#ffffff14;
      --text:#f8fafc;
      --muted:#cbd5e1;
      --accent:#38bdf8;
      --accent2:#facc15;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg1), var(--bg2));
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .wrap {
      width: min(900px, 100%);
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid #ffffff2a;
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.2vw, 2.1rem);
      color: var(--accent2);
    }

    p.sub {
      margin: 0 0 20px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .quote {
      margin: 14px 0;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
      background: #ffffff0d;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .text {
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 1.02rem;
    }

    .author {
      margin-top: 8px;
      color: #bae6fd;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: .92rem;
    }

    .tag {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 10px;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid #38bdf866;
      background: #38bdf826;
      color: #dff4ff;
      font-size: .8rem;
      letter-spacing: .2px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="wrap">
    <h1>🌟 Daily Inspiration</h1>
    <p class="sub">A few words to keep you moving forward, one day at a time.</p>

    <section class="quote">
      <p class="text">“Success is the sum of small efforts, repeated day in and day out.”</p>
      <div class="author">— Robert Collier</div>
    </section>

    <section class="quote">
      <p class="text">“It always seems impossible until it’s done.”</p>
      <div class="author">— Nelson Mandela</div>
    </section>

    <section class="quote">
      <p class="text">“You do not rise to the level of your goals; you fall to the level of your systems.”</p>
      <div class="author">— James Clear</div>
    </section>

    <section class="quote">
      <p class="text">“Great things are done by a series of small things brought together.”</p>
      <div class="author">— Vincent van Gogh</div>
    </section>

    <section class="quote">
      <p class="text">“Don’t watch the clock; do what it does. Keep going.”</p>
      <div class="author">— Sam Levenson</div>
    </section>

    <div class="footer">
      Build. Learn. Improve. Repeat. 🚀<br />
      <span class="tag">Powered by Harish's Docker Web Server</span>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
